Let's make a game!
	name:The Simpsons Clicked Out
	by:Liam
	desc:An Idle Game Based Off Of The Simpsons Tapped Out
	created:11/15/2018
	updated:11/15/2018
	
Buttons
	*bunnyButton1
		name:Make a bunny
		desc:Click this little bunny to get more bunnies!
		on click:anim icon wobble
		on click:yield 1 bunny
		on click:if (have goldenTouch and chance(1%)) yield 1 goldenCarrot
		icon:stuff/bunny.png
		no text
		class:bigButton hasFlares
		icon class:shadowed
		tooltip origin:bottom

	*bunnyButton
		name:Make a bunny
		desc:Click this little bunny to get more bunnies!
		on click:anim icon wobble
		on click:yield 1 bunny
		on click:if (have goldenTouch and chance(1%)) yield 1 goldenCarrot
		icon:stuff/bunny.png
		no text
		class:bigButton hasFlares
		icon class:shadowed
		tooltip origin:bottom

Resources
	*bunny|bunnies
		name:Bunny|Bunnies
		desc:These are your bunnies. You can use them to purchase things. Your goal is to have as many bunnies as possible!
		icon:icons[0,0]
		class:noBackground
		show earned
Buildings
	*TEMPLATE
		on click:anim glow
		
	*bunnyButton
		name:Rabbit cage|Rabbit cages
		desc:A tiny little cage.<//><b>Effect:</b><.>Produces 1 rabbit every 10 seconds.
		icon:icons[3,0]
		cost:15 bunnies
		on tick:yield 0.1 bunny
		unlocked